{
  "stem": "13382.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we shifted ourselves without Father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We all went back to-- not to Fil'akovo because that was a little village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we went back to the next bigger town, Lucenec.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we found some place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "There was a doctor/pediatrician who didn't come back and his house was available.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So we-- so we got-- we settled in and we started to sort of rebuild our lives there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know how much details I have, but things has started sort of improve somewhat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I think I'm going to talk about my personal things, which came out of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I mean, how I'm going to continue my life after-- after all this which I lived through.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The first-- my first contact after the liberation while still in Budapest was with a fellow by the name [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Kellerman, ?] Peter.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Kellerman, ?] Peter was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somewhat connected in the Communist sort of underground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And-- and when-- when we met, he said, listen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We are looking for people who can be trusted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Because in Hungary, by looks of it, no one can trust anymore, except the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because the Communist leaders from Russia will start to come in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And, you know, we have to sort of recreate some sort of a start for these things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And why-- why-- come with me to the [INAUDIBLE], which was the headquarters of that time, and join us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We need you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I mean, might as well do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a Communist sort of headquarters.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they give me a gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, I never shot anybody or anything in my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, I mean, it was sort of a part of dressing up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you-- you do certain work.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
